    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior shows well with a clean finish, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and light swirl marks consistent with regular washing. Inside, the cabin is tidy and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
