    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to disciplined ownership and consistent mechanical care. This unit has undergone a comprehensive technical evaluation to ensure peak operational performance and structural integrity. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the interior reflects a high standard of preservation. Offering a harmonious blend of reliability and sophisticated engineering, this vehicle is an ideal acquisition for those seeking lasting value without compromise. Detailed service records are available upon request to verify its excellent maintenance history.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
